comment: this gets soldered to plinky! you only need this if you have an original V1 plinky; later plinkys (may 2021) have this already installed.
break 24x1 into an8x2 and a 4x2; if you want to power separately, you should also get 10 more to make a 5x2
black thonk sockets for the CV outputs
green stereo thonk sockets for MIDI input/output
